- USB Wifi: urtwn0/run0 works 
 urtwn0: I-O DATA DEVICE, INC. (0x4bb) WN-G150UM (0x94c)
 pinebook: internal Wi-Fi not supported
 pinebook pro: internal bwfm0 works,sometimes hangs


